snippet.title: Hacking a coffee machine mr. robot style
snippet.description:
Hacking 101


So the aim of this video is to be a non-traditional tutorial. Within the video all the steps involved in replicating this should be outlined either by me saying it or by text on the screen. While simultaneously adding some nice cinematography to make it feel more like a movie than a tutorial. I hope I succeeded. Also if you have a better way of doing this please share, I know I personally would love any tips. I also think other people can benefit a lot from you sharing better solutions:) finally I am trying to almost completely replicate this scene from mr. robot https://youtu.be/zhvyK8q2Qtg
